# {{PROJECT_TITLE}} — project contract (mandatory)

The **user** (the person with the idea) is the designer / idea source. **Do not** ask the user to design repository layout, backup defaults, or “standard folder” choices — **you** follow this repo’s layout and [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md).

- **Implement** the user’s creative requests; capture inspiration in [DESIGN.md](DESIGN.md) and [ideas/INBOX.md](ideas/INBOX.md).
- **Maintain** git hygiene: commit **`package-lock.json`** whenever dependencies change; clear commit messages; suggest a **remote** when off-machine backup matters.
- **Verify** `npm run build` before declaring a task done.
